      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Ready to Ride \u2014 A Dependable Car in Good Condition! \u2014 Looking for a solid, trustworthy vehicle that's been well cared for? This car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 mechanically sound, regularly maintained, and ready for everyday driving. It's not brand new, but it's been looked after and shows it. No major issues to hide here \u2014 just a reliable ride at an honest price. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
