      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Exceptional Find \u2014 Mint Condition & Truly Turn-Key Ready! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in outstanding mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! It presents beautifully inside and out, with a pristine interior free of wear, a gleaming exterior with no notable blemishes, and mechanicals that feel tight and responsive. This is the kind of car that turns heads in a parking lot and gives you total confidence on the road. If you've been searching for a vehicle that's as close to showroom-fresh as the used market gets, your search ends here. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
      "price": 46500.0,
