    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. This is a truly exceptional example that stands apart from the typical used car offering. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with no visible scratches, chips, or dents to speak of. Panel gaps are tight and consistent, and all trim pieces, badges, and moldings are perfectly intact. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the dealer lot \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface is clean and unmarked. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, fluid levels are properly maintained, and the vehicle runs with a smooth, confident power delivery. The tires have strong tread remaining and the brakes are in excellent shape. This is the kind of used car that makes buyers do a double-take \u2014 a genuinely pristine, move-in-ready vehicle that requires absolutely nothing before driving away. If you've been searching for the best available example on the market, your search ends here.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. This car presents as virtually flawless, inside and out. The exterior paint is deep, glossy, and free of scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Body panels are perfectly aligned, trim is intact, and all glass is clear and chip-free. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells fresh \u2014 no stains, no tears, no worn spots on the seats, carpets, or headliner. All electronics, controls, and comfort features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. Tires have strong tread remaining and wear evenly. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and shows it in every detail. Ideal for a buyer who wants a car they can drive with pride from day one, with no surprises.",
      "price": 45000.0,
